# Courses
POST http://localhost:3000/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "slug": "demo-course",
  "title": "Demo Course",
  "description": "Demo",
  "published": true
}

###
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/courses/demo-course
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title"
}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/courses/demo-course/modules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Module 1",
  "description": "Intro"
}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/modules/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "moduleIdsInOrder": ["mod1","mod2"]
}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/modules/{{MODULE_ID}}/lessons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Lesson 1",
  "type": "TEXT",
  "textContent": "Hello"
}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "moduleId": "{{MODULE_ID}}",
  "lessonIdsInOrder": ["les1","les2"]
}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/courses/demo-course/enrol
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/{{LESSON_ID}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

###
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me/lessons/next
